messages.message: Agree with the point about table which we've added in the copy. We can gather more feedback and see if "reasoning" resonates with users. cc @melissa.amos

Regarding other examples mentioned above
• Extracting 5 data points and returning a JSON object: can we address this with data type? @lydia @Jianqi Xing
• Extracting a single data point where you need to provide more context: an example is captured in Taxdown video. What’s our guidance on what users should do this such cases? @Sławek Biel 
• Extracting a paragraph of text - for example a clause in a contract: can we support this with data type? @lydia @Jianqi Xing
